improvements.tr_note_01: Te mau reo ’āpī i ’āmui-hia mai: Te reo tūra’i nō Pura’itira, Reo Tahiti
Hi’opo’a i te mau nūmera tātari nō te tāvini-ra’a i rāfa’i e te mau pupu reo i roto i te mau parau fā’ito a te feiā poro
improvements.tr_note_02: Tāpiri te fa'atupura'a āmuri i te tā'atira'a tāta'ira'a
improvements.tr_note_03: Ua fa'ahou-hia te pu'e haere i ni'a 'e ua tāpiri-hia te pūpū ohipa i raro nā te uira'a tāmau'a (mobile)
improvements.tr_note_04: Fa'aîe atu te mau hora o te mau taeae orero fa'ahiti ei PDF
